he%20Election%20Commission%20and%20use%20of%20EVMs%20(electronic%20voting%20machines)%20in%20various%20posts%20and%20videos.%20This%20led%20to%20complaints%20from%20political%20groups%2C%20although%20no%20legal%20action%20was%20officially%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742819520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fpsfq6gbo_kunal-kamra_625x300_24_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-times-when-comedian-kunal-kamra-ran-into-controversies-7999668%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20Mumbai%20event%20was%20disrupted%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20leaders%20on%20Sunday%20after%20he%20made%20jokes%20that%20were%20seen%20as%20directed%20at%20their%20party%20chief%20and%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Paul%20and%20Paulette%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Souleymane%E2%80%99s%20Story%E2%80%99%20Win%20Top%20Honors%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20Red%20Lorry%20Film%20Festival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742819270000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FPaul-and-Paulette-Take-a-Bath.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236346255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BookMyShow%E2%80%99s%20Red%20Lorry%20Film%20Festival%20crowned%20Venice%20winner%20%E2%80%9CPaul%20and%20Paulette%20Take%20a%20Bath%E2%80%9D%20and%20Cannes-winning%20%E2%80%9CSouleymane%E2%80%99s%20Story%E2%80%9D%20as%20winners%20of%20its%20competition%20segment%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20as%20the%20sophomore%20edition%20of%20the%20Indian%20international%20film%20festival%20wrapped%20after%20three%20days%20of%20packed%20screenings%20across%20Mumbai.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20Nevanka%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20the%20Critics%E2%80%99%20Pick%20a