%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Army%20is%20partnering%20with%20Lyft%20and%20Uber%20for%20a%20military%20base%20access%20pilot%20program.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pilot%20aims%20to%20improve%20transportation%20for%20over%20600%2C000%20personnel%20on%20six%20Army%20bases.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20successful%2C%20the%20initiative%20could%20expand%20to%20over%2020%20military%20bases%20nationwide.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20wants%20to%20open%20its%20base%20gates%20to%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20drivers%20to%20give%20soldiers%20more%20options%20for%20getting%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20partnership%20and%20pilot%20program%20starting%20Monday%20morning%20involving%20the%20US%20Army%20and%20ride-share%20companies%20Lyft%20and%20Uber%20seeks%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20drivers%20approved%20to%20enter%20six%20military%20bases.%20The%20program%20aims%20to%20expand%20driver%20opportunities%20and%20improve%20transportation%20for%20troops%20on%20and%20off%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20military%20bases%20is%20normally%20only%20granted%20to%20servicemembers%2C%20their%20families%2C%20and%20government%20civilians.%20Now%2C%20company%20drivers%20without%20any%20government%20affiliation%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20base%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222430dfe9-d45f-4f16-8d7e-5e33c43b6d04%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesting%20the%20waters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20pilot%20program%2C%20currently%20set%20to%20last%20just%20two%20months%2C%20will%20initially%20focus%20on%20six%20Army%20installations%20home%20to%20over%20600%2C000%20service%20members%2C%20families%2C%20and%20government%20civilians%2C%20Uber%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocations%20include%20Fort%20Bliss%20in%20Texas%2C%20Fort%20Bragg%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Joint%20Base%20Lewis-McChord%20in%20Washington%2C%20and%20three%20base%20locations%20in%20Hawaii.%20If%20the%20new%20program%20is%20successful%2C%20the%20Army%20hopes%20to%20expand%20the%20initiative%20to