ment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223672b20f-6d6e-4a3a-80b6-c2e21f5359e1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it's%20going%20to%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20and%20Lyft%20drivers%20approved%20for%20military%20base%20access%20will%20receive%20a%20base%20access%20credential%20which%20could%20be%20digital%20or%20physical%2C%20according%20to%20an%20Army%20spokesman.%20But%20they%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20access%20base%20without%20an%20official%20work%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20must%20display%20their%20ride%20requests%20on%20their%20phones%20to%20military%20gate%20guards%2C%20proving%20they%20are%20servicing%20a%20rider%20who%20already%20has%20base%20access%20credentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20choose%20to%20opt%20in%20must%20pass%20the%20Army's%20base%20access%20vetting%20process%2C%20including%20an%20in-person%20background%20check%2C%20according%20to%20Uber.%20Such%20checks%20are%20normally%20performed%20at%20a%20military%20base's%20visitor%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20additional%20incentives%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20ride-app%20drivers%20who%20can%20seek%20on-base%20credentialing%2C%20beyond%20expanding%20their%20pool%20of%20riders%20to%20base%20personnel.%20To%20gain%20base%20approval%2C%20they'll%20have%20to%20head%20to%20base%20access%20centers%20on%20their%20own%20dime%20and%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joint%20Base%20Lewis-McChord's%20Liberty%20Gate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddd9f4b8b41a9673fb6fe2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoint%20Base%20Lewis-McChord's%20Liberty%20Gate.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20photo%2C%20Joint%20Base%20Lewis-McChord%20Public%20Affairs%20Office%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20will%20also%20aim%20to%20hold%20a%20military%20recruiting%20drive%20to%20boost%20contract%20employment%20for%20on-base%20personnel%20seeking%20to%20