oing%20budget%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament.%20The%20earlier%20revision%20of%20the%20salary%20and%20allowances%20paid%20to%20sitting%20and%20former%20MPs%20was%20announced%20in%20April%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20base%20pay%20for%20an%20MP%20announced%20in%20the%20revision%20in%202018%20was%20Rs%201%2C00%2C000%20per%20month.%20The%20purpose%20of%20setting%20this%20amount%20was%20to%20bring%20their%20salary%20into%20line%20with%20the%20rates%20of%20inflation%20and%20the%20growing%20cost%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202018%20revision%2C%20MPs%20receive%20an%20allowance%20of%20Rs%2070%2C000%20as%20constituency%20allowance%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20costs%20of%20keeping%20their%20offices%20up%20to%20date%20and%20interacting%20with%20voters%20in%20their%20respective%20districts.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20they%20receive%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20month%20as%20office%20allowance%20and%20Rs%202%2C000%20as%20a%20daily%20allowance%20during%20Parliamentary%20sessions.%20These%20allowances%20will%20also%20be%20increased%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20MPs%20also%20get%20an%20allowance%20annually%20for%20phone%20and%20internet%20usage.%20They%20enjoy%2034%20free%20domestic%20flights%20per%20year%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20families%2C%20and%20first%20class%20train%20travel%20at%20any%20time%20for%20professional%20and%20personal%20use.%20They%20can%20also%20claim%20mileage%20allowance%20when%20they%20use%20roads.%20MPs%20also%20enjoy%20the%20benefits%20of%2050%2C000%20free%20units%20of%20electricity%20and%204%2C000%20kilolitres%20of%20water%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20takes%20care%20of%20their%20housing%20and%20accommodation%20too.%20During%20their%20five-year%20term%2C%20MPs%20are%20provided%20with%20rent-free%20housing%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20They%20could%20get%20hostel%20rooms%2C%20apartments%2C%20or%20bungalows%20based%20on%20their%20seniority.%20Individuals%20who%20opt%20not%20to%20utilise