%20on%20politicians%2C%20they%20demolish%20the%20venue.%20If%20you%20do%20it%20on%20cricketers%20or%20actors%2C%20their%20fans%20and%20PR%20army%20abuses%20you%20for%20two%20months.%20If%20you%20do%20crowdwork%2C%20intellectuals%20say%20it's%20not%20real%20comedy.%20If%20you%20do%20it%20on%20your%20wife%2C%20woke%20people%20call%20you%20sexist.%20If%20you%20do%20it%20on%20your%20parents%2C%20some%20say%20you%20are%20discourteous.%20Haathi%2C%20cheenti%2C%20please%20come%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20evergreen%20elephant-ant%20jokes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHabitat%20studio%20is%20a%20preferred%20venue%20for%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20by%20popular%20comics.%20It%20made%20headlines%20last%20month%20too%2C%20when%20YouTuber%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20made%20crass%20remarks%20at%20a%20roast%20show%2C%20India's%20Got%20Latent%2C%20shot%20at%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20studio%20management%20said%20they%20had%20decided%20to%20shut%20the%20premises%20for%20now%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20they%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20views%20of%20the%20artists%20performing%20on%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shocked%2C%20worried%20and%20extremely%20broken%20by%20the%20recent%20acts%20of%20vandalism%20targeting%20us.%20Artists%20are%20solely%20responsible%20for%20their%20views%20and%20creative%20choices.%20We%20have%20never%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20content%20performed%20by%20any%20Artist%2C%20but%20the%20recent%20events%20have%20made%20us%20rethink%20about%20how%20we%20get%20blamed%20and%20targeted%20every%20time%20almost%20like%20we%20are%20a%20proxy%20for%20the%20performer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shutting%20down%20till%20we%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20way%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20free%20expression%20without%20putting%20ourselves%20and%20our%20property%20in%20jeopardy.%20We%20invite%20all%20artists%2C%20audience%20and%20stakeholders%20to%20discuss%20and%20share%20their%20views%20freely%20and%20request%20your%20guidance%20so%20that%20we%20also%20respect%20the%20performers'%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20studio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20studio%20had%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20that%20it%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20making%20of%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20latest%20video%20and%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20endorse%20the%20views%20expressed%20by%20it%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20extend%20a%20sincere%20and%20heartfelt%20apology%20to%20all%20those%20hurt%20by%20this%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20after%20a%20group%20of%20Sena%20workers%20entered%20the%20premises%20in%20Khar%20and%20damaged%20property%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20comic's%20remarks%20against%20Mr%20Shinde.%20Visuals%20showed%20Sena%20workers%20swinging%20chairs%20at%20cameras%2C%20lights%20and%20speakers%20at%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20show%20shot%20last%20month%2C%20Kunal%20Kamra%20targeted%20Mr%20Shinde%20with%20a%20parody%20version%20of%20'Bholi%20Si%20Surat'%2C%20a%20popular%20song%20from%20the%201997%20blockbuster%20Dil%20To%20Pagal%20Hai.%20He%20used%20the%20'gaddar'%20(traitor)%20jibe%20against%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%2C%20who%20led%20a%20rebellion%20against%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20in%202022%2C%20bringing%20down%20his%20government%20and%20splitting%20the%20party.%20Multiple%20FIRs%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20comic%2C%20including%20one%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20minister%20Pratap%20Sarnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742812980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjhf95gn_abijit-ganguly_625x300_24_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkunal-kamra-eknath-shinde-habitat-studio-abijit-ganguly-comics-basic-common-sense-post-over-shiv-senas-mumbai-studio-rampage-7997371%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earlier%20today%2C%20Habitat%20Studio's%20management%20announced%20that%20it%20ha