india-news%2Fkunal-kamra-told-mumbai-cops-he-does-not-regret-his-remarks-sources-7997684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra%20has%20told%20Mumbai%20Police%20he%20does%20not%20regret%20his%20comment%20about%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Monday%20afternoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkunal-kamra-told-mumbai-cops-he-does-not-regret-his-remarks-sources-7997684%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Freedom%20Of%20Speech%2C%20Only%20Action%26quot%3B%3A%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20On%20Kunal%20Kamra%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20row%20over%20stand-up%20comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20recent%20remarks%2C%20several%20political%20figures%2C%20including%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MPs%20have%20come%20forward%20to%20defend%20Mr%20Kamra's%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20criticise%20the%20actions%20of%20those%20who%20vandalised%20the%20Mumbai%20venue%20where%20his%20show%20was%20filmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bachchan%20questioned%20the%20limits%20placed%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%20restriction%20on%20speaking%2C%20what%20will%20become%20of%20you%3F%20You%20are%20anyway%20in%20a%20bad%20situation.%20There%20are%20restrictions%20on%20you.%20You%20would%20be%20told%20to%20speak%20just%20on%20this%20and%20nothing%20else%2C%20that%20do%20not%20interview%20Jaya%20Bachchan%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Bachchan%20told%20reporters%20outside%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20is%20freedom%20of%20speech%3F%20There%20is%20freedom%20of%20action%20only%20when%20there%20is%20a%20ruckus%20-%20beat%20up%20the%20opposition%2C%20rape%20women%2C%20murder%20them.%20What%20else%3F%20You%20%5BEknath%20Shinde%5D%20left%20your%20real%20party%20and%20formed%20another%20party%20for%20power.%20Isn't%20that%20an%20insult%20of%20Balasaheb%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20actor-turned-politician%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Arvind%20Sawant%20came%20out%20in%20defence%20of%20Mr%20Kamra%2C%20saying%20every%20remark%20made%20by%20the%20comedian%20in%20his%20comedy%20special%2C%20Naya%20Bharat%2C%20was%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20what%20Kunal%20Kamra%20did%2C%20I%20think%20every%20word%2C%20every%20sentence%20said%20by%20him%20is%20correct.%20That%20is%20what%20everyone%20in%20Opposition%20is%20alleging%20against%20him.%20He%20said%20that%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20poem.%20If%20we%20say%20there%20is%20democracy%20in%20this%20country%20and%20we%20believe%20in%20that%2C%20then%20we%20must%20accept%20all%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sawant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sawant%20drew%20comparisons%20to%20the%20past%2C%20referencing%20Shiv%20Sena%20founder%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray's%20legacy%20as%20a%20cartoonist%2C%20who%20often%20made%20caricatures%20of%20prominent%20political%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCriticism%20is%20criticism.%20Sometimes%2C%20someone%20does%20mimicry.%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%20was%20a%20renowned%20cartoonist%3B%20he%20made%20caricatures%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20Nehru.%20Had%20it%20been%20the%20present%20time%2C%20they%20would%20have%20filed%20cases%20against%20him%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sawant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20for%20action%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20vandalising%20the%20Habitat%20Comedy%20Club%20in%20Khar%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20Mr%20Kamra's%20show%20was%20filmed.%20%26quot%3BFIR%20should%20be%20registered%20against%20those%20who%20vandalised...%20Can't%20they%20accept%20criticism%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20voiced%20her%20condemnation%2C%20calling%20the%20vandalism%20an%20example%20of%20growing%20intolerance%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20ignited%20a%20fire%20like%20this%20in%20Nagpur.%20They%20are%20now%20doing%20this%20in%20Mumbai.%20What%20kind%20of%20intolerance%20is%20this%3F%20If%20you%20don't%20like%20something%2C%20file%20a%20Police%20complaint%20but%20if%20there%20is%20such%20behavior%2C%20I%20think%20people%20of%20Mumbai%20are%20watching%3B%20Maharashtra%20is%20watching%20how%20law%20and%20order%20is%20being%20taken%20into%20hand%2C%20and%20they%20have%20stooped%20to%20hooliganism%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Chaturvedi%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20controversy%20was%20over%20a%20joke%20that%20did%20not%20even%20directly%20mention%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister's%20name%2C%20but%20rather%20hinted%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20threatening%20over%20a%20joke%20where%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20name%20was%20not%20even%20mentioned%3B%20only%20the%20intelligent%20would%20have%20gotten%20the%20hint%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Chaturvedi%2C%20the%20response%20to%20Mr%20Kamra's%20joke%20only%20reflected%20the%20underlying%20truth%20in%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20at%20Habitat%20Comedy%20Club%20in%20Mumbai%20escalated%20when%20a%20group%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde)%20youth%20wing%20entered%20the%20venue%20while%20another%20live%20show%20was%20ongoing%2C%20forced%20the%20show%20to%20be%20shut%20down%2C%20and%20caused%20significant%20damage%20to%20the%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20since%20been%20filed%20against%20both%20Mr%20Kamra%20for%20his%20controversial%20remarks%20and%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20for%20the%20vandalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sub%20inspector%20Vijay%20from%20Khar%20police%20station%2C%20the%20group%20targeted%20the%20venue%20after%20Mr%20Kamra's%20stand-up%20special%20Naya%20Bharat%20was%20released.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20y