ll%20determine%20if%20the%20children%20have%20allergies%20and%20what%20they%20like%20in%20their%20full-time%20nanny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20yacht%2C%20I%20check%20out%20the%20Facebook%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fyachtiesnameshameandfame%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYachties%3A%20Name%2C%20Shame%2C%20and%20Fame%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20if%20there's%20anything%20to%20know%20before%20I%20accept%20any%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20time%20I've%20turned%20a%20job%20down%20is%20when%20the%20child%20has%20a%20medical%20issue%20I'm%20not%20qualified%20to%20deal%20with.%20At%20sea%2C%20you%20can't%20get%20to%20a%20hospital%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b90be65e-c1df-4425-bc7a-983fc9f2fde9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20differences%20between%20working%20as%20a%20nanny%20on%20a%20yacht%20and%20on%20land%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESafety%20is%20critical%20%E2%80%94%20many%20families%20will%20always%20wear%20lifejackets%2C%20and%20plans%20can%20change%20quickly%20due%20to%20bad%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20land%2C%20you've%20got%20house%20managers%20and%20PAs%20to%20liaise%20with.%20On%20water%2C%20the%20captain%20is%20in%20charge%2C%20and%20the%20chain%20of%20command%20must%20be%20followed%20for%20safety%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20must%20also%20help%20the%20children%20adapt%20to%20life%20on%20board.%20They're%20used%20to%20going%20to%20the%20bathroom%20alone%20or%20getting%20a%20drink%2C%20but%20a%20galley%20filled%20with%20chefs%20cooking%20can%20be%20dangerous.%20They%20can%20get%20trapped%20in%20a%20bathroom%20if%20they're%20not%20strong%20enough%20to%20open%20a%20fire%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20look%20after%20one%20or%20two%20children.%20The%20most%20I've%20looked%20after%20is%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4de0f69-273b-43c3-ada6-f6a6e1c5db0a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wake%20up%20at%206%20a.m.%20each%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20a%20coffee%20and%20updates%20from%20the%20crew%20before%20the%20children%20wake.%20I'll%20usually%20take%20the%20children%20jet%20skiing%20or%20wakeboarding%20in%20the%20morning%20after%20breakfast.%20I%20like%20the%20children%20to%20wear%20orange%20swimwear%2C%20so%20it's%20easier%20to%20spot%20them%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20afternoon%2C%20we%20may%20play%20board%20games%2C%20do%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20or%20decorate%20cupcakes.%20To%20prepare%20them%20for%20the%20next%20destination%2C%20I'll%20learn%20some%20fun%20facts%20about%20the%20next%20country%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20any%20dinosaurs%20used%20to%20live%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20parents%20just%20want%20to%20enjoy%20peace%20and%20quiet%2C%20but%20they'll%20always%20participate%20in%20the%20pirate%20treasure%20hunt.%20We%20usually%20pretend%20the%20captain%20has%20been%20taken%20hostage%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20so%20much%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20we'll%20have%20a%20movie%20night%20under%20the%20stars.%20Last%20year's%20favorite%20movie%20was%20Wonka%2C%20so%20I%20created%20a%20Wonka-style%20dessert%20bar%20for%20the%20children%20to%20enjoy%20while%20watching%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBedtime%20can%20be%20at%207%20p.m.%20or%2011%20p.m.%20The%20rules%20disappear%20because%20everyone's%20on%20holiday%20and%20just%20having%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d6d9f7c-15e6-4e0d-9ad2-0fa1b1b12c10%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20charters%20take%20place%20in%20Cannes%2C%20Nice%2C%20St.%20Tropez%2C%20and%20Sardinia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20route%20is%20popular%20because%20it's%20beautiful%2C%20well%20mapped%20out%2C%20and%20the%20weather%20is%20pretty%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20jet-skied%20between%20the%20Faraglioni%20rocks%20in%20Capri%2C%20joined%20one%20family%20for%20a%20private%20tour%20of%20the%20Acropolis%2C%20and%20had%20a%20charter%20in%20the%20Adriatic%2C%20where%20a%20barge%20was%20brought%20out%2C%20and%20we%20were%20treated%20to%20a%20private%20fireworks%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20visiting%20Rovinj%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-visit-croatia-felt-like-italy-but-better-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECroatia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20local%20children%20run%20around%20the%20port%20and%20play%20together%3B%20sometimes%2C%20the%20kids%20I'm%20with%20will%20join.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce175071-8b47-4b2d-ac40-2dd217f50db0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20job%20is%20the%20connections%20you%20build%20with%20the%20families%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20downside%20to%20being%20a%20nanny%20is%20that%20you%20reach%20a%20point%20when%20the%20children%20don't%20need%20you%20anymore.%20We%20keep%20in%20touch%20with%20Christmas%20cards%2C%20and%20if%20they're%20in%20London%2C%20we%20will%20meet%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20days%20I%20find%20challenging%20are%20the%20last%2C%20as%20I%20don't%20like%20to%20say%20goodbye%2C%20and%20the%20first%20day%2C%20because%20the%20children%20are%20excited%20to%20be%20on%20board%20and%20have%20so%20much%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20get%20lonely%2C%20but%20if%20I%20miss%20home%20and%20have%20five%20minutes%20to%20call%20a%20friend%2C%20I'll%20catch%20up%20with%20them%2C%20and%20then%20I'm%20good%20to%20go%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d1c457a-0a93-4ce8-ab80-495b55040ce3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20turned%20this%20into%20my%20own%20business%20to%20help%20others%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20I%20launched%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsuperyachtnanny.co%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuperyacht%20nanny.co%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0where%20I%20offer%20coaching%20sessions%20to%20other%20nannies%20and%20produce%20online%20guides.%20I%20charge%20%24106%20for%20a%2045-minute%20coaching%20session.%20I%20plan%20to%2