20of%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%20Under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20Sankar%20had%20to%20pay%20his%20wife%20around%20Rs%209%20crore%20and%20Rs%204.3%20lakh%20per%20month%20and%20share%20a%20joint%20custody%20of%20their%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fkg11i3f_sankar_625x300_24_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Image%20credit%3A%20x.com%2Fmyprasanna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Dhivya%20negotiated%20with%20him%20to%20come%20to%20Chennai%20and%20share%20their%20son's%20custody%20-%20which%20did%20happen%20for%20some%20time%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20tensions%20escalated%20between%20the%20two%20when%20his%20wife%20refused%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20MoU%20-%20especially%20over%20depositing%20their%20child's%20passport%20in%20a%20shared%20locker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20started%20claiming%20that%20the%20MOU%20is%20not%20valid%20and%20she%20wants%20more%20and%20will%20go%20to%20the%20US%20again%20to%20file%20a%20divorce%2C%20Sankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resulted%20in%20a%20further%20legal%20battle%20with%20Sankar%20approaching%20the%20courts%20saying%20he%20will%20only%20share%20the%20custody%20of%20their%20son%20after%20the%20passport%20is%20deposited%20in%20the%20locker.%20%26quot%3BShe%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20courts.%20Instead%20she%20showed%20up%20to%20my%20hotel%20at%2010%20PM%20in%20the%20night%20and%20calls%20my%20son%20to%20the%20lobby%20for%2010%20minutes%20luring%20him%20which%20I%20stopped.%20She%20then%20chose%20to%20call%20the%20police%20and%20filed%20a%20kidnapping%20complaint%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFearing%20wrongful%20arrest