2Fus%2Fgeorge-clooney-fought-hard-for-sleepy-joes-election-and-then-dumped-him-like-a-dog-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F119411461.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhoni%20Makes%20Big%20CSK%20Captaincy%20Revelation%2C%20Says%20%26quot%3BMost%20Important%20Calls...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERejecting%20speculation%20that%20he%20is%20the%20back-room%20decision-maker%20in%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20despite%20handing%20over%20captaincy%20to%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%2C%20the%20talismanic%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20said%20he%20is%20instead%20focussed%20on%20reinventing%20himself%20and%20his%20strokes%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%20relevant%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20IPL.%20Speaking%20to%20'JioStar'%20after%20CSK's%20four-wicket%20win%20over%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20their%20lung-opener%20on%20Sunday%20night%20here%2C%20Dhoni%20spoke%20about%20the%20team%20dynamics%20under%20Gaikwad%2C%20his%20own%20form%20and%20also%20the%20regional%20commentary%20being%20done%20in%20the%20ongoing%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...batsmen%20are%20now%20willing%20to%20take%20risks.%20They%20believe%20that%20with%20proper%20cricketing%20shots%2C%20they%20can%20play%20big%20strokes%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20are%20improvising%20with%20their%20shot%20selection...whether%20it's%20a%20reverse%20scoop%20against%20a%20fast%20bowler%2C%20a%20sweep%2C%20or%20a%20reverse%20sweep%20against%20a%20pacer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20no%20different%2C%20I%20have%20to%20adapt%20as%20well.%20This%20is%20what%20is%20required%20of%20me%20for%20where%20I%20am%20batting.%20You%20have%20to%20try%20and%20stay%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhoni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20we%20played%20T20%20in%202008%20and%20the%20way%20we%20played%20IPL%20last%20year%2C%20it's%20very%20different.%20Earlier%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20turn%20in%20the%20wickets.%20Wickets%20were%20two-paced.%20Now%2C%20India's%20wickets%20have%20become%20much%20better%3B%20they%20are%20more%20batter-friendly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2043-year-old%2C%20under%20whom%20CSK%20won%20five%20IPL%20titles%2C%20handed%20over%20the%20leadership%20to%20Gaikwad%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%202024%20season.%20He%20said%20although%20he%20discusses%20things%20with%20Gaikwad%2C%20he%20refrains%20from%20persuading%20him%20to%20follow%20his%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRuturaj%20has%20been%20part%20of%20us%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20His%20temperament%20is%20very%20good%2C%20he's%20very%20calm%2C%20very%20composed.%20So%20those%20were%20the%20reasons%20we%20considered%20him%20for%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20I%20also%20told%20him%2C%20'If%20I%20give%20you%20advice%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20have%20to%20follow%20it.%20I%20will%20try%20to%20stay%20away%20as%20much%20as%20possible.'%20During%20the%20season%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20speculated%20that%20I%20was%20making%20the%20decisions%20in%20the%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhoni%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20fact%20is%2C%20he%20was%20making%2099%20percent%20of%20the%20decisions.%20The%20most%20important%20calls%20--%20bowling%20changes%2C%20field%20placements%20--%20were%20all%20his.%20I%20was%20just%20helping%20him%20out.%20He%20did%20a%20brilliant%20job%20of%20handling%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20player%20with%20whom%20Dhoni%20shares%20a%20close%20bond%20is%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20star%20and%20national%20batting%20mainstay%20Virat%20Kohli.%20The%20veteran%20said%20their%20relationship%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20strong%20friendship%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20always%20an%20honest%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20--%20whether%20a%20certain%20approach%20was%20right%20or%20if%20an%20adjustment%20could%20have%20been%20made.%20Initially%2C%20it%20was%20more%20of%20a%20relationship%20between%20a%20captain%20and%20a%20young%20player%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20as%20we%20kept%20interacting%2C%20we%20became%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20today%2C%20we%20share%20that%20bond%2C%20though%20there's%20always%20a%20line%20of%20respect%20between%20a%20senior%20and%20a%20junior.%20Now%20that%20neither%20of%20us%20is%20captain%2C%20we%20get%20more%20time%20to%20talk%20before%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20cricketer%20was%20quite%20pleased%20with%20the%20IPL%20broadcasters'%20decision%20to%20have%20regional%20commentary%20for%20the%20immensely%20popular%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...listening%20to%20commentary%20gives%20you%20an%20outsider's%20perspective.%20It%20sparks%20new%20ideas%20like%20'why%20don't%20we%20try%20this%20approach%3F'...which%20can%20then%20be%20evaluated%20based%20on%20intelligence%20and%20data%20to%20see%20if%20it%20fits%20within%20the%20team's%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20heard%20a%20lot%20of%20regional%20commentary%2C%20but%20I%20know%20that%20Bihari%20(Bhojpuri)%20commentary%20is%20highly%20energetic.%20It%20reminds%20me%20of%20old-school%20radio%20commentary%2C%20where%20the%20commentators%20were%20very%20involved.%20I%20find%20that%20very%20interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742800320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fqhg4memo_ms-dhoni-interview_625x300_24_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fms-dhoni-makes-big-csk-captaincy-revelation-says-most-important-calls-7996848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20is%20officially%20the%20captain%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20some%20fans%20f