ts%20during%20their%20ongoing%20and%20acrimonious%20custody%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Prasanna%20Sankar%2C%20his%20wife%20has%20falsely%20accused%20him%20of%20rape%2C%20domestic%20violence%2C%20and%20kidnapping%2C%20allegedly%20using%20her%20connections%20within%20the%20police%20to%20harass%20him.%20In%20response%2C%20Sankar%20has%20accused%20her%20of%20abducting%20their%209-year-old%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMy%20name%20is%20Prasanna%2C%20who%20previously%20founded%20Rippling%20(worth%20%2410B)%3B%20I'm%20going%20through%20a%20divorce.%20I'm%20now%20on%20the%20run%20from%20the%20Chennai%20police%20hiding%20outside%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20This%20is%20my%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Prasanna%20S%20(%40myprasanna)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmyprasanna%2Fstatus%2F1903802958187544687%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2023%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Prasanna%20Sankar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasanna%20Sankaranarayanan%20is%20an%20Indian-origin%20entrepreneur%20based%20in%20Singapore.%20Born%20and%20raised%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20he%20earned%20a%20Bachelor's%20degree%20in%20Computer%20Science%20from%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Tiruchirappalli%20(NIT%20Trichy)%2C%20where%20he%20also%20met%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESankar%20is%20a%20well-known%20figure%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20best%20recognised%20as%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Rippling%2C%20a%20workforce%20management%20software%20company%20currently%20valued%20at%20around%20%2410%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20launching%20Rippling%2C%20he%20gained%20experience%20at%20leading%20tech%20firms%2C%20including%20an%20internship%20at%20Google%20in%202006%20and%20a%20subsequent%20role%20at%20Microsoft%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20January%202023%2C%20Sankar%20has%20also%20been%20the%20founder%20of%200xPPL%2C%20a%20decentralized%20social%20network%20designed%20for%20crypto%20communities%2C%20as%20per%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20his%20passion%20for%20programming%2C%20Sankar%20shares%20on%20LinkedIn%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20programming%20contests%3A%20I%20was%20ranked%20%231%20in%20India%20at%20TopCoder%20while%20in%20college%2C%20was%20a%20two-time%20Google%20Code%20Jam%20world%20finalist%2C%20and%20a%20two-time%20ACM%20ICPC%20world%20finalist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742800020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fqfsjiq9_prasanna-sankar_625x300_24_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-prasanna-sankar-all-about-rippling-co-founder-caught-in-custody-battle-with-wife-7997010%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Prasanna%20Sankar%2C%20his%20wife%20has%20falsely%20accused%20him%20of%20rape%2C%20domestic%20violence%2C%20and%20kidnapping.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-prasanna-sankar-all-about-rippling-co-founder-caught-in-custody-battle-with-wife-7997010%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amanda%20Seyfried%20Talks%20Her%20%E2%80%98F%E2%80%94%26nbsp%3Bed%20Up%E2%80%99%20Character%20in%20Series%20Mania%20Title%20%E2%80%98Long%20Bright%20River%2C%E2%80%99%20Calls%20for%20Compassion%20for%20Victims%20of%20Addiction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742799600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FLONGBRIGHTRIVER2025_Eps101.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236346058%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amanda%20Seyfried%20admired%20her%20%E2%80%9Cfear