e%20retreat.%20And%2C%20the%20sparrows%20and%20squirrels%20never%20failed%20to%20check%20in%20on%20him.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20I%20think%20of%20it%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20probably%20how%20I%20tided%20through%20that%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202008%20that%20Rakesh%2C%20realising%20that%20the%20corner%20office%20would%20never%20rival%20the%20happiness%20he%20felt%20when%20he%20was%20around%20birds%2C%20decided%20to%20turn%20all%20his%20attention%20to%20nest-making.%20And%20the%20accolades%20that%20followed%20%E2%80%94%20the%20National%20Science%20Award%20(2020)%2C%20mention%20in%20the%20Limca%20Book%20of%20World%20Records%20(2018)%2C%20the%20International%20Green%20Apple%20Award%20(2013)%2C%20Earth%20Day%20Network%20Star%20(2020)%2C%20membership%20with%20the%20IUCN%20(2020)%2C%20and%20being%20named%20%E2%80%98Earth%20Champion%E2%80%99%20by%20Sony%20BBC%20Earth%20(2025)%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F248135%2Fbihar-arvind-mishra-great-adjutant-stork-garuda-wildlife-conservation-endangered-species-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtributions%20to%20bird%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20were%20proof%20of%20the%20ripples%20of%20the%20impact%20his%20work%20was%20creating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20change%20through%20empowerment%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Rakesh%20received%20a%20letter.%20It%20was%20from%20an%2085-year-old%20Bengaluru-based%20gynaecologist%20whom%20he%20had%20taught%20to%20make%20a%20nest.%20The%20letter%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20d